          <p>
            My love for technology began early. As a kid, I was <em>always creating, drawing, making music, and experimenting with making games</em>. In high school, I got my first taste of programming and realized: this could actually become my career.
          </p>

          <img src="/assets/images/gaya-norway.webp" alt="">

